SUMMARY:AI for Business Professionals Workshop
DESCRIPTION:All Things AI (Live)\n**Overview**\nIn just one day\, transfor
 m the way you work with the Artificially Intelligent Operating System for 
 Professionals.\nThis hands-on training equips business professionals with 
 the practical skills to master generative AI tools\, accelerate productivi
 ty\, and stay ahead in an AI-driven economy.\nYou won’t just learn *what
 * AI can do. You’ll learn *how* to use it to do more\, faster—with les
 s friction and more clarity.\n\n*[To purchase tickets\, visit [https://202
 6.allthingsai.org/register](https://2026.allthingsai.org/register) worksho
 p tickets also include access to the All Things AI conference on March 24t
 h. Price increases after Tuesday\, March 17 so sign-up early and save $100
  ]*\n\n**What You’ll Learn**\n\n* **Master ChatGPT**\n\nUnderstand how i
 t works\, when to trust it\, and how to prompt it for precision\, insight\
 , and speed.\n* **Compare Leading Chatbot Platforms: Claude vs. Gemini**\n
 \nSee how Claude\, Gemini (Google DeepMind) differ in philosophy\, capabil
 ity\, and integration\n* **Deploy Your Own AI Agents**\n\nLearn how agent-
 based systems can automate knowledge work and create leverage in sales\, m
 arketing\, and operations.\n* **Create Your Own Productivity Playbook**\n\
 nApply what you’ve learned to your own role\, with frameworks for using 
 AI daily and staying ahead of change.\n\nThis course is built for knowledg
 e workers\, managers\, and business leaders—not AI researchers. No jargo
 n. Just results.\n**Who Should Attend**\n\n* Professionals seeking a compe
 titive edge\n* Teams aiming to integrate AI into their daily workflows\n* 
 Leaders who want to confidently drive AI strategy across their organizatio
 ns\n\n**By the end of the day\, you’ll:**\n\n* Understand how large lang
 uage models like ChatGPT work and how to apply them safely\n* Be fluent in
  prompting best practices and conversational design\n* Use Claude\, ChatGP
 T\, and Gemini strategically based on business fit\n* Deploy AI agents to 
 offload repetitive tasks\n* Walk away with a customized AI action plan tai
 lored to your work\n\n**Be an AI Leader**\nAI isn’t coming. It’s alrea
 dy reshaping your industry.\nBut the advantage doesn’t go to the biggest
  company. It goes to the team that learns the fastest.\nThis course gives 
 you that advantage.\n\n**[To purchase tickets\, visit [https://2026.allthi
 ngsai.org/register](https://2026.allthingsai.org/register) workshop ticket
 s also include access to the All Things AI conference on March 24th. Price
  increases after Tuesday\, March 17 so sign-up early and save $100 ]**
