SUMMARY:Major League Hacking AI Roadshow at All Things AI 2026
DESCRIPTION:All Things AI (Live)\n[Major League Hacking (MLH)](https://mlh
 .io/) is bringing their builder-focused AI Roadshow to [All Things AI](htt
 ps://2026.allthingsai.org) on March 23-24 at the Durham Convention Center.
  This is your chance to try out new AI developer tools\, check out live de
 mos\, and connect with fellow builders.\nThis is a free event within All T
 hings AI\, but you do need to be registered.\n\nThe MLH AI Roadshow is des
 igned with students in mind — anyone 16 and up is welcome\, though atten
 dees under 18 need to be accompanied by an adult. Professionals and adult 
 builders are absolutely welcome too.\n\nThere are two sessions on Monday 
 — a morning event and an afternoon event. We ask that you only RSVP to o
 ne so we can give everyone a chance to participate.\n\nRegistration is req
 uired via **[Eventbrite](https://www.eventbrite.com/e/all-things-ai-confer
 ence-tickets-1088254772319?aff=oddtdtcreator&_gl=1%2A1030zg4%2A_ga%2AMTkzM
 DgyMTUyMi4xNzcxMTYyODU2%2A_ga_Z1T7KGQP7R%2AczE3NzIyMDc3ODkkbzMzJGcxJHQxNzc
 yMjEwNTkxJGo2MCRsMCRoMA..)** to gain access to the event.\n\nAnd if you wa
 nt to stick around for the full All Things AI conference on Tuesday the 24
 th\, use the code **MLH** for 20% off your registration! You can also use 
 this direct link to apply the discount automatically: [www.eventbrite.com/
 e/1088254772319/?discount=MLH](http://www.eventbrite.com/e/1088254772319/?
 discount=MLH)\n\nDon't just talk about the future of AI — come help us b
 uild it!\nDetails and registration for the MLH AI Roadshow: [https://2026.
 allthingsai.org/major-league-hacking-ai-roadshow](https://2026.allthingsai
 .org/major-league-hacking-ai-roadshow)
